oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Billy Grammer Job No. 36359
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Grammer, Billy; Martin, Jimmy;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 921) for an order placed by Billy Grammer for 6 orders of 50 two color window cards for a performance by Billy Grammer and Jimmy Martin at San Rafael High School in San Rafael, California on February 9, Richmond Union High School in San Pablo, California on February 10, the Oakland Civic Auditorium in Oakland, California on February 11, Santa Cruz High School in Santa Cruz, California on February 12, Fremont High School in Sunnyvale, California on February 13, and Salinas High School in Salinas, California on February 15. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
